<script>
var audioTag = document.querySelectorAll('.bs-audioField-audioJs audio');
for (var i = 0; i < audioTag.length; i++) {
  audioTag[i].addEventListener('play', function () {
    dataLayer.push({
      'event': 'ga.audio',
      'eventAction': 'play',
      'eventLabel': this.getAttribute('src'),
    });
  });
    audioTag[i].addEventListener('pause', function () {
    dataLayer.push({
      'event': 'ga.audio',
      'eventAction': 'pause',
      'eventLabel': this.getAttribute('src'),
    });
  });
  
}
</script>

<script>
document.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
  var link = e.target.closest('a');
  if (!!link) {
	dataLayer.push({
      event: 'ga.social',
      socialNetwork: link.title,
      socialAction: 'Click Social Profile Link',
      socialTarget: link.href,
    });
  }  
});
</script>
